      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not required at MRL 2; qualitative equivalency between validation and COU inputs documented.",
      "rationale": "Quantitative equivalency analysis of input parameters between the validation domain and the COU is not required at MRL 2. A qualitative assessment confirms that fluid properties, geometric features, and operating conditions in the validation experiments are representative of the COU application envelope. This is documented in the credibility assessment report."
